## RED -- Never Available

These are Lodewijk's personal credentials. They are not shared during the event. Do not ask for them.

- Supabase Executive Vault keys (Loom KB, CFO data, client ICP data)
- Supabase Team Operations service key
- Stripe live key (sk_live_...)
- HubSpot personal access token
- Discord bot token
- Loom session cookie
- Google Workspace OAuth credentials
- Google Ads refresh token
- Meta/Facebook Ads access token

If your bounty seems to require one of these, talk to Thanh. There is always a sandbox alternative.

